======================================================================
WHY IS TOTAL=3 IMPOSSIBLE?
======================================================================

Checking: does t₃=3 always force c₅≥1 at n=6?
  Cases with t₃=3 at n=6:
    t₃=3, c₅=1: 2880 tournaments
  YES: t₃=3 always has c₅≥1 at n=6!

